---
title: Plant-Based Crumbed Chicken & Katsu Sauce with Corn Rice & Creamy Slaw
description: A golden crumb demands a top tier sauce to accompany it and these plant-based crumbed chicken tenders need just that.
Let’s introduce the star of tonight’s dinner, katsu sauce, perfect for drizzling over these chick’n bites and corn rice.
